ORIGINAL TOOL CREDITS:
This CLI tool is based on the original SNI-Spoofing tool by @patterniha.
The original tool was a Windows-only application using WinDivert for
kernel-level packet manipulation.

This version has been reimplemented as a cross-platform CLI tool using
pure userspace techniques, making it compatible with Windows, macOS, and Linux.

Telegram: @patterniha
USDT (BEP20): 0x76a768B53Ca77B43086946315f0BDF21156bF424
